<item>
            <title>[LU-5879] Tell interested people when a section of code they are interested in has a proposed change</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5879</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Individuals often have particular interests in specific areas of code (a file or directory).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When a patch arrives in Gerrit that will change this are of code, the individual should receive an email to inform them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="27496">LU-5879</key>
            <summary>Tell interested people when a section of code they are interested in has a proposed change</summary>
